example.statement:
Determine the limits for the following functions:



		\ds \lim_{x\to 5^+} \dfrac{x+1}{x-5}




		\ds \lim_{x\to 5^-} \dfrac{x+1}{x-5}




		\ds \lim_{x\to 2\pi^+} x\csc x
